Package: subtools
Type: Package
Title: Read and Manipulate Video Subtitles
Version: 1.0
Date: 2019-11-28
Authors@R: c(
      person("Francois", "Keck", email = "francois.keck@gmail.com", role =  c("aut", "cre")),
      person("Bob", "Rudis", email = "bob@rud.is", role = "ctb",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5670-2640"))
    )
Maintainer: Francois Keck <francois.keck@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of functions to read, write and manipulate video subtitles.
    Supported formats include "srt", "subrip", "sub", "subviewer", "microdvd", 
    "ssa", "ass", "substation", "vtt", and "webvtt".
